Class PTEID_Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.gov.cartaodecidadao.PTEID_Object
      • pt.gov.cartaodecidadao.PTEID_Address
  • public class PTEID_Address
extends PTEID_Object
    Class for the Address document on a EID Card.
    You can get such an object from PTEID_EIDCard::getAddr().
